insights.description: Well-structured Riksbyggen annual report with clear sections
insights.impact: Standard layout made extraction straightforward and reliable

insights.description: Financial statements clearly presented with consistent formatting
insights.impact: High-quality source data resulted in 95% high-confidence extractions

insights.description: Board member information clearly listed with roles and mandate years
insights.impact: Governance agents extracted data with very high confidence (0.96-0.98)

insights.description: Comprehensive notes section with detailed breakdowns (Note 4 - Driftkostnader had 12+ line items)
insights.impact: Operational agent able to extract granular cost breakdown

insights.description: Loan table (Note 13) provided complete details: rates, maturity, amortization schedule
insights.impact: Loans agent extracted full loan structure with high confidence

challenges.issue: No cash flow statement present in annual report
challenges.resolution: Marked as no data found - common for smaller BRFs
challenges.future_guidance: Cash flow statements optional for small BRFs, don't flag as error

challenges.issue: No energy class rating visible in document
challenges.resolution: Extracted energy costs from operational breakdown instead
challenges.future_guidance: Energy class not always required; focus on cost data as fallback

challenges.issue: Annual fee change rate mentioned in 2012, not recent
challenges.resolution: Extracted historical reference with medium confidence (0.92)
challenges.future_guidance: When fee changes are historical, note date and reduce confidence slightly

recommendations_for_future: Riksbyggen reports follow consistent format - use template matching for faster processing
